# ğŸ¥ Nabd Platform â€“ UI/UX Project Timeline

This repository documents the **UI/UX design process** for a our Medical App Nabd.  
The project is divided into **phases**, each with clear deliverables.  

---

## ğŸ“… Project Timeline (8 Weeks)

### **Phase 1: Research & Discovery (Week 1â€“2)**
- Define problem statement
- Identify target users (patients, doctors, caregivers)
- Stakeholder analysis (RACI Matrix + Power/Interest Grid)
- Competitor research (study 2â€“3 medical apps)
- Build user personas (2â€“3 personas)
- SWOT analysis of app idea
- Define requirements:
  - Business goals
  - User goals
  - Functional requirements
  - Non-functional requirements

**Deliverables:**
- Problem statement document
- Target users table
- RACI + Power/Interest diagrams
- Competitor research report
- User persona cards
- SWOT table
- Requirements list

---

### **Phase 2: Information Architecture (Week 3)**
- Define user flows (appointments, reminders, emergency)
- Create navigation map (sitemap)
- Content strategy (what goes on each screen)

**Deliverables:**
- User flow diagrams
- App navigation map
- Content outline

---

### **Phase 3: Wireframing (Week 4)**
- Low-fidelity wireframes
- Mid-fidelity wireframes
- Clickable prototype (basic)

**Deliverables:**
- Wireframe sketches
- Mid-fidelity wireframes (Figma/Balsamiq)
- Prototype link

---

### **Phase 4: Visual Design (Week 5)**
- Moodboard (colors, fonts, medical imagery)
- Style guide / design system
- High-fidelity mockups (core screens)

**Deliverables:**
- Moodboard file
- Style guide
- High-fidelity mockups (Home, Appointments, Reminders, Emergency)

---

### **Phase 5: Prototyping (Week 6)**
- High-fidelity mockups for all screens
- Interactive prototype in Figma

**Deliverables:**
- Clickable high-fidelity prototype link
- Screen-by-screen walkthrough

---

### **Phase 6: Usability Testing (Week 7)**
- Prepare test scenarios
- Run tests with 3â€“5 participants
- Collect feedback & refine design

**Deliverables:**
- Usability test report
- Prototype refinements

---

### **Phase 7: Final Documentation & Handoff (Week 8)**
- Compile full project report
- Prepare presentation slides
- Optional: record demo video

**Deliverables:**
- Final report (PDF/Word)
- Presentation slides (PPT/Canva)
- Demo video (optional)
- GitHub repo with process + designs

---

